### Google's Campus Recruitment Online Assessment Pattern

Google's campus recruitment for new grads (e.g., 2026 hiring) typically begins with profile-based recruiter outreach or Google Kickstart contests, followed by online assessments or direct phone screens focusing heavily on **Data Structures & Algorithms (DSA)**, with no dedicated aptitude sections in technical rounds.[1][2]

#### 1. Overall Difficulty Level
**Medium to Hard.** Initial phone/online screens feature 1 medium or 2 easy DSA pr
